---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Practice Materials">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-10 py-20 text-center">
		
		<div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-12">
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">Preparation & Practice</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-light">Competition math should always be challenging, not intimidating. We encourage all students to feel prepared. Explore our sample problem sets and historical data packets below to understand the unique analytical style and pacing of the Integrated Mathematics Tournament.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
			
			<div class="bg-brand-light border-2 border-brand-gold rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-inner hover:shadow-card-hover hover:scale-[1.03] transition duration-300 group">
				<div class="bg-brand-gold text-brand-dark text-xs font-bold uppercase px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full inline-block mb-5 shadow-sm">Signature Round</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-gold transition">2024 Mock Data Set: Pandemic Modeling</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 text-base mb-8 line-clamp-3 font-light">A simulated power round analyzing viral transmission rates using authentic public health data.</p>
				<button class="w-full bg-brand-dark text-brand-light font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition group-hover:scale-105 transform">Download PDF Packet</button>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover hover:scale-[1.03] transition duration-300 group hover:border-slate-300">
				<div class="bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 text-xs font-bold uppercase px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full inline-block mb-5 shadow-sm">Team Round</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-dark transition">Sample 10-Question Team Test</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 text-base mb-8 line-clamp-3 font-light">A standard 40-minute collaborative test covering diverse analytical topics.</p>
				<button class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-700 transition group-hover:scale-105 transform">Download PDF Packet</button>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover hover:scale-[1.03] transition duration-300 group hover:border-brand-green">
				<div class="bg-brand-green text-brand-light text-xs font-bold uppercase px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full inline-block mb-5 shadow-sm">Individual Round</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-green_dark transition">Algebra Mock Test: Functions</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 text-base mb-8 line-clamp-3 font-light">10 rigorous problems focusing on functional equations and complex polynomials.</p>
				<button class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-700 transition group-hover:scale-105 transform">Download PDF Packet</button>
			</div>

            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover hover:scale-[1.03] transition duration-300 group hover:border-brand-green">
				<div class="bg-brand-green text-brand-light text-xs font-bold uppercase px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full inline-block mb-5 shadow-sm">Individual Round</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-green_dark transition">Geometry Mock Test: Depth</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 text-base mb-8 line-clamp-3 font-light">10 challenging questions covering Euclidean proofs, trigonometry, and spatial reasoning.</p>
				<button class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-700 transition group-hover:scale-105 transform">Download PDF Packet</button>
			</div>

            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover hover:scale-[1.03] transition duration-300 group hover:border-brand-green">
				<div class="bg-brand-green text-brand-light text-xs font-bold uppercase px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full inline-block mb-5 shadow-sm">Individual Round</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-green_dark transition">Number Theory Mock Test</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 text-base mb-8 line-clamp-3 font-light">10 questions analyzing prime factorization, modular arithmetic, and Diophantine equations.</p>
				<button class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-700 transition group-hover:scale-105 transform">Download PDF Packet</button>
			</div>

            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover hover:scale-[1.03] transition duration-300 group hover:border-brand-green">
				<div class="bg-brand-green text-brand-light text-xs font-bold uppercase px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full inline-block mb-5 shadow-sm">Individual Round</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-green_dark transition">Combinatorics Mock Test</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 text-base mb-8 line-clamp-3 font-light">10 challenging questions involving advanced counting principles and graph theory basics.</p>
				<button class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-700 transition group-hover:scale-105 transform">Download PDF Packet</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>